hadiths[141]{hadithnumber,text}:
735,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz shuru kartey waqt apne donon hathon ko kandhon tak uthaatey, isi tarah jab rukoo ke liye (Allaahu-akbar) kehtey aur jab apna sar rukoo se uthatey to donon hath bhi uthatey (rafa' yadain kartey) aur rukoo se sar Mubarak uthatey huey ( سمع الله لمن حمده , Mina padhi. ربنا ولك الحمد ( kehtey they. sajde mein jatey waqt rafa'-yadain nahi kartey they."
736,jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey huey to takbeer tahreema ke waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rafa'-yadain kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke donon hath us waqt moondhon ( kandhon ( tak uthey aur isi tarah jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo ke liye takbeer kehtey us waqt bhi) rafa'-yadain ( kartey. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kehtey ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( albatta sajde mein aap rafa'-yadain nahi kartey they.
737,"jab wo Namaz shuru kartey to takbeere-tahreema ke sath rafa'-yadain kartey, phir jab rukoo mein jatey us waqt bhi rafa'-yadain kartey aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey tab bhi kartey aur unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kya kartey they."
738,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz takbeer tahreema se shuru kartey aur takbeer kehtey waqt apne donon hathon ko kandhon tak utha kar ley jatey aur jab rukoo ke liye takbeer kehtey tab bhi isi tarah kartey aur jab ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey tab bhi isi tarah kartey aur) ربنا ولك الحمد ( kehtey. sajda kartey waqt ya sajdey se sar uthatey waqt is tarah rafa'-yadain nahi kartey they.
739,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Namaz mein dakhil hotey to pahley takbeer tahreema kehtey aur sath hi rafa'-yadain kartey. isi tarah jab wo rukoo kartey tab aur jab ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey tab bhi) rafa'-yadain kartey ( donon hathon ko uthatey aur jab Qada اولیٰ se uthtey tab bhi rafa'-yadain kartey. aap ne us amal ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaayaa. (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah Namaz padha kartey they.)
740,"logon ko hukm diya jata tha ke Namaz mein dayan hath baain kalaaii par rakhein , abu-Hazim bin-Dinar ne bayan kya ke mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke aap usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaatey they. Ismail bin abi ovais ne kaha ke ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchai jati thi yun nahi kaha ke pahunchaatey they."
741,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke, kya tum samajhtey ho ke mera munh idhar (qible ki taraf) hai. Allah ki qism tumhara rukoo aur tumhara khushoo mujh se kuchh chipa hua nahi hai, main tumhen apne peechhey se bhi dekhta rehta hun."
742,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya rukoo aur sujood poori tarah kya karo. Allah ki qasam! main tumhen apne peechhey se bhi dekhta rehta hon ya is tarah kaha ke peeth peechhey se jab tum rukoo kartey ho aur sajda kartey ho (to main tumhen dekhta hun ( .
743,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( se shuru kartey they.
744,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takbeer tahreema aur qirat ke darmyan thodi der chup rahtey they. Abu-Zaraa ne kaha, main samajhta hun Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap par mere maan-baap fidaa hun. aap us takbeer aur qirat ke darmyan ki khamoshi ke beech mein kya padhtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main padhta hon اللهم باعد بيني وبين خطاياى كما باعدت بين المشرق والمغرب ، Mina padhi. اللهم نقني من الخطايا كما ينقى الثوب الأبيض من الدنس ، Mina padhi. اللهم اغسل خطاياى بالماء والثلج والبرد aey Allah ! mere aur mere gunahon ke darmyan itni doori kar jitni mashriq aur maghrib mein hai. aey Allah ! mujhey gunahon se is tarah paak kar jaisey safaid kapda mail se paak hota hai. aey Allaah! mere gunahon ko paanii, barf aur oley se dho daal."
745,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suraj gehen ki Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khadey huey to der tak khadey rahe phir rukoo mein gaey to der tak rukoo mein rahe. phir rukoo se sar uthaya to der tak khadey hi rahe. phir ( dobara ( rukoo mein gaey aur der tak rukoo ki haalat mein rahe aur phir sar uthaayaa, phir sajda kya aur der tak sajde mein rahe. phir sar uthaya aur phir sajda kya aur der tak sajde mein rahe phir khadey huey aur der tak khadey hi rahe. phir rukoo kya aur der tak rukoo mein rahe. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar uthaya aur der tak khadey rahe. phir (dobaara) rukoo kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) der tak rukoo ki haalat mein rahe. phir sar uthaayaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein chaley gaey aur der tak sajde mein rahe. jab Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya ke jannat mujh se itni nazdeek ho gaee thi ke agar main chahta to iske khoshon mein se koi khosha tum ko tod kar la deta aur mujh se dozakh bhi itni qareeb ho gaee thi ke main bol padaa ke mere Malik main to usmein se nahi hoon? maine wahan aik aurat ko dekha. Naafe bayan kartey hain ke mujhey khayal hai ke ibne-abi-Mulaika ne batlaya ke us aurat ko aik billi nauch rahi thi, maine puchha ke uski kya wjah hai? jawab mila ke us aurat ne us billi ko baandhey rakha tha yahan tak ke bhook ki wjah se wo mar gaee, na to usne usey khana diya aur na chhoda ke wo khud kahin se kha letii. Naafe ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke ibne-abi-Mulaika ne yun kaha ke na chhoda ke wo zameen ke keedey wghaira kha letii."
746,kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki rakaton mein (faatiha ke siwaa) aur kuchh qirat kartey they? unhon-ne farmaya ke haan. ham ne kaha ke aap log ye baat kis tarah samajh jatey they. farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ke hilney se.
747,jab wo ( sahaba ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rukoo se sar uthaney ke baad us waqt tak khadey rahtey jab tak dekhtey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein chaley gaey hain (is waqt wo bhi sajdey mein jatey ( .
748,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein suraj gehen hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gehen ki Namaz padhi. logon ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! ham ne dekha ke (namaz mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se kuchh leney ko aagey badhey they phir ham ne dekha ke kuchh peechhey hatey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine jannat dekhi to usmein se aik khosha lena chaha aur agar main ley leta to us waqt tak tum usey khaatey rahtey jab tak duniya maujood hai.
749,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko Namaz padhai. phir member par tashrif laey aur apne hath se qible ki taraf ishara karke farmaya ke abhi jab main Namaz padha raha tha to jannat aur dozakh ko us diwar par dekha. uski tasweerein us diwar mein qible ki taraf namudaar huin to maine aaj ki tarah khair aur shar kabhi nahi dekhi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaule-mazkoor teen baar farmaya.
750,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, logon ka kya haal hai jo Namaz main apni nazrein aasman ki taraf uthatey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se bahut hi zyada sakhti se rokaa. yahan tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke log us harkat se baaz aa jayen warna unki beenaaii uchak li jaeygi."
751,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhney ke barey mein poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to daaka hai jo shaitan bandey ki Namaz par daalta hai.
752,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dhaarii daar chadar mein Namaz padhi. phir farmaya ke iske naqsh w nigaar ne mujhey ghaafil kar diya. usey ley ja kar abu-Jaheem ko wapas kar do aur unse (bajaaey iske) saadii chadar maang laao.
753,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein qible ki diwar par raint dekhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt logon ko Namaz padha rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (namaz hi mein) raint ko khurch dala. phir Namaz se farigh honey ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi Namaz mein hota hai to Allah Taala iske munh ke samney hota hai. isliye koi shakhs samney ki taraf Namaz mein na thookey . us hadis ki riwayat Musa-bin-Aqba aur Abdul-Azeez ibne-abi Rawaad ne Naafe se ki.
754,"(Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wafat k marz mein) musalman fajr ki Namaz padh rahe they, achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre se parda hataya . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko dekha. sab log safain baandhey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (khushii se) khub khul kar muskuraaey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh kar) peechhey hatna chaha taake saf mein mil jaaein. aap ne samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la rahe hain. sahaba (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh kar khushi se is qadr be-qaraar huey ke maano) Namaz hi chhod dengey. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishara kya ke apni Namaz poori kar lo aur parda daal liya. isi din chasht ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wafat paaii."
755,"ahale-koofa ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ki umr Faarooq (Raziallahu anhu) se shikayat ki. isliye umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko hataakar Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Kufa ka Hakim banaya, to Kufa walon ne Sad ke mutaalliq yahan tak keh diya ke wo to achi tarah Namaz bhi nahi padha saktey. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko bula bhejaa. aap ne unse puchha ke aey Abu-Is'haaq! un Kufa walon ka khayal hai ke tum achi tarah Namaz nahi padha saktey ho. is par aap ne jawab diya ke Allah ki qasam! main to unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ki tarah Namaz padhaataa tha, usmein kotahi nahi karta isha ki Namaz padhaataa to uski 2 pehli rakaat mein (qir'at) lambi karta aur dusri 2 rakatein halki padhaataa. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aey Abu-Ishaq ! mujh ko tum se ummeed bhi yahi thi. phir aap ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aik ya kai aadmiyon ko Kufa bhejaa. qaasid ne har-har masjid mein ja kar unke mutaalliq poochha. sab ne aap ki tareef ki lekin jab masjid banii-Abbas mein gaey. to aik shakhs jiska naam Usaama-bin-Qataada aur kunniyat Abu-Sa'ada thi khada hua. usne kaha ke jab aap ne Allah ka waasta de kar puchha hai to (suniye ke) Sad na fauj ke sath khud jihad kartey they, na maale-ghanimat ki taqseem sahi kartey they aur na faisley mein adl w insaf kartey they. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ye sun kar) farmaya ke Allah ki qism main ( tumhari is baat par) teen duaein karta hun. aey Allaah! agar tera ye banda jhoota hai aur sirf dikhawey ke liye khada hua hai to uski umr-daraaz kar aur usey khub mohtaaj bana aur usey fitnon mein mubtala kar. iske baad (wo shakhs us darja bdhaal hua ke) jab us se puchha jata to kehta ke aik boodha aur pareshan haal hon mujhey Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki baddua lag gaee. Abdul-Malik ne bayan kya ke maine usey dekha uski bhawein budhapey ki wjah se aankhon par aa gaee thi. lekin ab bhi raston mein wo ladkiyon ko chhedtaa ."
756,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis shakhs ne sura Fatiha na padhi uski Namaz nahi hui."
757,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laey iske baad aik aur shakhs aaya. usne Namaz padhi, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. aap ne salam ka jawab de kar farmaya ke wapas jao aur phir Namaz padh, kyonke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. wo shakhs wapas gaya aur pahley ki tarah Namaz padhi aur phir aa kar salam kya. lekin aap ne us martaba bhi yahi farmaya ke wapas ja aur dobara Namaz padh, kyonke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. aap ne is tarah teen martaba kya. aakhir us shakhs ne kaha ke us zaat ki qasam! jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya hai. main iske ilawa aur koi achchha tariqa nahi janta, isliye aap mujhey Namaz sikhaa dijiye. aap ne farmaya ke jab Namaz ke liye khada ho to pahley takbeer tahreema keh. phir aasani ke sath jitna Quran tujh ko yad ho uski tilawat kar. iske baad rukoo kar, achi tarah se rukoo ho ley to phir sar utha kar poori tarah khada ho jaa. iske baad sajda kar poorey itminan ke saath. phir sar utha aur achi tarah baith jaa. isi tarah apni tamam Namaz poori kar."
758,"main in (koofa waalon) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah Namaz padhaataa tha. Zohar aur Asr ki donon namaazein, kisi qism ka naqs unmein nahi chhorta tha. pehli 2 rakatein lambi padhta aur dusri 2 rakatein halki . to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujh ko tum se ummeed bhi yahi thi."
759,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki pehli 2 rakaton mein sura Fatiha aur har rakaat mein eik-eik sura padhtey they, unmein bhi qirat kartey they lekin aakhiri 2 rakatein halki padhatey they kabhii-kabhii ham ko bhi koi aayat suna diya kartey they. Asr mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sura Fatiha aur soortein padhtey they, uski bhi pehli 2 rakatein lambi padhtey. isi tarah subah ki Namaz ki pehli rakaat lambi kartey aur dusri halkii."
760,"kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein qirat kya kartey they? to unhon-ne batlaya ke haan, ham ne puchha ke aap logon ko kis tarah malum hota tha? farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ke hilney se."
761,kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki namazon mein qirat kya kartey they? to unhon-ne kaha ke haan! maine kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qirat karne ko aap log kis tarah malum kar letey they? farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ke hilney se.
762,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki 2 rakaat mein sura Fatiha aur eik-eik sura padhtey they. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi kabhii koi aayat hamein suna bhi diya kartey.
763,umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) (unki maan ( ne unhein (Sura Mursalaat) padhtey huey suna. phir kaha ke aey betey ! tum ne is sura ki tilawat karke mujhey yad dilaayaa. mein aakhir umr main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maghrib mein yahi sura padhtey huey suntii thi.
764,Zaid-bin-Saabit ne mujhey tokaa ke tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke tum maghrib mein chhoti chhotii soortein padhtey ho. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 lambi Suraton mein se aik sura padhtey huey suna.
765,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maghrib mein sura taur padhtey huey suna tha.
766,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath isha ki Namaz padhi. usmein aap ne ( إذا السماء انشقت‏ ( padhi aur sajda ( tilawat ( kya. maine unse iske mutaalliq malum kya to batlaya ke maine abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey bhi (is aayat mein tilawat ka ( sajda kya hai aur zindagi bhar mein usmein sajda karunga, yahan tak ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mil jaun."
767,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein they ke isha ki 2 pehli rakaat mein se kisi aik rakaat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( والتين والزيتون‏ ( padhi.
768,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath isha padhi, aap ne ( إذا السماء انشقت‏ (aur sajda kya. is par maine kaha ke ye sajda kaisa hai? aap ne jawab diya ke is sura mein maine abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey sajda kya tha. isliye main bhi hamesha usmein sajda karunga, yahan tak ke aap se mil jaun."
769,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isha main ( والتين والزيتون‏ ( padhtey suna. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada achi awaz ya achi qirat wala kisi ko nahi paya.
770,"ameerul-momineen umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap ki shikayat Kufa walon ne tamam hi baton mein ki hai, yahan tak ke Namaz mein bhii. unhon-ne kaha ke mera amal to ye hai ke pehli 2 rakaat mein qirat lambi karta hun aur dusri 2 mein mukhtasar jis tarah maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi thi usmein kisi qism ki kami nahi karta. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke sach kehtey ho. tum se ummeed bhi isi ki hai."
771,main apne bap ke sath abu-Barza Aslami sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya. ham ne aap se Namaz ke waqton ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz suraj dhalney par padhtey they. Asr jab padhtey to Madina ke intihai kinara tak aik shakhs chala jata. lekin suraj ab bhi baqi rahtaa. maghrib ke mutaalliq jo kuchh aap ne kaha wo mujhey yad nahi raha aur isha ke liye tehai raat tak der karne mein koi harj mehsus nahi kartey they aur aap us se pahley soney ko aur uske baad baat cheet karne ko na-pasand kartey they. jab Namaz subah se farigh hotey to har shakhs apne qareeb baithey huey ko pehchan sakta tha. aap donon rakaat mein ya aik mein sath se lekar so tak aayatein padhtey.
772,"har Namaz mein Quran Majeed ki tilawat ki jaeygi. jin main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Quran sunaya tha ham bhi tumhen unmein sunaengey aur jin namazon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aahista qirat ki ham bhi unmein aahista hi qirat karengey aur agar sura Fatiha hi padho jab bhi kafi hai, lekin agar zyada padh lo to aur behtar hai."
773,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba chand sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Ukaaz ke bazar ki taraf gaey. un dinon shayatin ko aasman ki khabrein leney se rok diya gaya tha aur un par angaarey ( Shahab Saqib ( phainkey janey lagey they. to wo shayatin apni qaum ke paas aaey aur puchha ke baat kya hui. unhon-ne kaha ke hamein aasman ki khabrein leney se rok diya gaya hai aur (jab ham aasman ki taraf jatey hain to ( ham par shahaabe-Saqib phainkey jatey hain. shayatin ne kaha ke aasman ki khabrein leney se rokney ki koi nai wjah hui hai. isliye tum mashriq w maghrib mein har taraf phail jao aur us sabab ko malum karo jo tumhen aasman ki khabrein leney se rokney ka sabab hua hai. wjah malum karne ke liye nikley huey shayatin tahaama ki taraf gaey jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ukaaz ke bazar ko jatey huey maqam nakhla main apne ashaab ke sath namaaze-fajr padh rahe they. jab Quran Majeed unhon-ne suna to ghaur se uski taraf kaan laga diye. phir kaha, Allah ki qasam! yahi hai jo aasman ki khabrein sunney se rokney ka baais bana hai. phir wo apni qaum ki taraf lautey aur kaha qaum ke logo! ham ne hairat-angez Quran suna jo seedhey rastey ki taraf hidayat karta hai. isliye ham is par eman latey hain aur apne rab ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraatey. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat nazil hui ( قل أوحي إلى‏ ( (aap kahey ke mujhey wahi ke zariey bataya gaya hai) aur aap par jinon ki guftgu wahi ki gaee thi."
774,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jin namazon mein buland awaz se Quran Majeed padhney ka hukm hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein buland awaz se padha aur jin mein aahista se padhney ka hukm hua tha unmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aahista se padha aur tera rab bhoolney wala nahi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi tumharey liye behtreen namoona hai.
775,aik shakhs Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke maine raat aik rakaat mein mufassal ki sura padhi. aap ne farmaya ke kya isi tarah (jaldii-jaldii) padhi jaisey sher padhey jatey hain. main un ek jaisi Suraton ko janta hun jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik sath mila kar padhtey they. aap ne mufassal ki bees Suraton ka zikr kya. har rakaat ke liye 2-2 soortein.
776,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki 2 pehli rakaton mein sura Fatiha aur 2 soortein padhtey they aur aakhiri 2 rakaat mein sirf sura Fatiha padhtey . kabhi kabhii hamein aik aayat suna bhi diya kartey they aur pehli rakaat mein qirat dusri rakaat se zyada kartey they. Asr aur subah ki Namaz mein bhi aap ka yahi mamool (routine) tha.
777,kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein Quran Majeed padhtey they? unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan! ham ne puchha ke aapko malum kis tarah hota tha. unhon-ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ke hilney se.
778,"mujh se Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada ne bayan kya, wo apne walid abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki 2 pehli rakaton mein sura Fatiha aur koi aur sura padhtey they. kabhi kabhii Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi aayat hamein suna bhi diya kartey they. pehli rakaat mein qirat zyada lamba kartey they."
779,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki pehli rakaat mein (qir'at) lamba kartey they aur dusri rakaat mein mukhtasar. subah ki Namaz mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah kartey they.
780,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab imam ( Aameen ( kahey to tum bhi) Aameen ( kaho. kyonke jiski ( Aameen ( malaaika ke Aameen ke sath ho gaee iske pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jaengey. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Aameen ( kehtey they.
781,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi tum mein se ( Aameen ( kahey aur farishton ne bhi usi waqt aasman par) Aameen ( kahi . is tarah aik ki) Aameen ( doosrey ke) Aameen (ke sath mil gaee to iske pichhley tamam gunah maaf ho jatey hain.
782,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kahey to tum bhi) Aameen ( kaho kyonke jisne farishton ke sath ( Aameen ( kahi uske pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. Sumaii ke sath us hadis ko Muhammad-bin-Amr ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya aur Nuaim Mujmir ne bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
783,"wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf (namaz padhney ke liye) gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt rukoo mein they. isliye saf tak pahunchne se pahley hi unhon-ne rukoo kar liya, phir iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya ke Allah tumhara shauq aur zyada karey lekin dobara aisa na karna."
784,unhon-ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Basra mein aik martaba Namaz padhi. phir kaha ke hamein unhon-ne wo Namaz yad dila di jo ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padha kartey they. phir kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab sar uthatey aur jab sar jhukaatey us waqt takbeer kehtey.
785,"aap logon ko Namaz padhatey they, to jab bhi wo jhuktey aur jab bhi wo uthtey takbeer zaroor kehtey. phir jab farigh hotey to farmatey ke main Namaz padhney main tum sab logon se zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz se mushabihat (similarity) rakhney wala hun."
786,"maine aur Imran-bin-Husain ne Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey Namaz padhi. to wo jab bhi sajda kartey to takbeer kehtey. isi tarah jab sar uthatey to takbeer kehtey. jab 2 rakaat ke baad uthtey to takbeer kehtey. jab Namaz khatm hui to Imran-bin-Husain ne mera hath pakad kar kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne aaj Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz yad dilai , ya ye kaha ke us shakhs ne ham ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ki tarah aaj Namaz padhai."
787,"maine aik shakhs ko maqaame-Ibraaheem mein (namaz padhtey huey) dekha ke har jhukney aur uthney par wo takbeer kehta tha. isi tarah khadey hotey waqt aur baithtey waqt bhii. maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko uski itlaa di. aap ne farmaya, arey teri maan marey ! kya ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki si Namaz nahi hai."
788,"maine Makka mein aik boodhey ke peechhey (zuhar ki) Namaz padhi. unhon-ne (tamaam Namaz mein) baaiis takbeerein kahiin. is par maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke ye boodha bilkul be aql malum hota hai Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya tumhari maan tumhen roey ye to abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai. aur Moosaa-bin-Ismaaeel ne yun bhi bayan kya ke ham se Aban ne bayan kya, ke kaha ham se Qatada ne, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Ikrima ne ye hadis bayan ki."
789,"unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to takbeer kehtey. phir jab rukoo kartey tab bhi takbeer kehtey they. phir jab sar uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey aur khadey hi khadey ( ربنا لك الحمد‏ ( kehtey. phir jab (doosrey) sajde ke liye jhuktey tab takbeer kehtey aur jab sajde se sar uthatey tab bhi takbeer kehtey. isi tarah aap tamam Namaz poori kar letey they. Qada اولیٰ se uthney par bhi takbeer kehtey they. (is hadis mein) Abdullaah-bin-Saaleh ne Leis ke waastey se (bajaaey ( ربنا لك الحمد‏ ( ke) ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( naql kya hai. ( ربنا لك الحمد‏ ( kahey ya ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( واؤ ke sath tareeqe durust hain)."
790,maine apne walid ke pahlu mein Namaz padhi aur apni donon hatheliyon ko mila kar raanon ke darmyan rakh liya. is par mere bap ne mujhey tokaa aur farmaya ke ham bhi pahley isi tarah kartey they. lekin baad mein us se rok diye gaey aur hukm hua ke ham apne hathon ko ghutnon par rakhein.
791,Huzaifa-bin-Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik shakhs ko dekha ke na rukoo poori tarah karta hai na sajda. isliye aap ne us se kaha ke tum ne Namaz hi nahi padhi aur agar tum mar gaey to tumhari maut us sunnat par nahi hogi jis par Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko paida kya tha.
792,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rukoo w sujood , donon sajdon ke darmyan ka waqfa aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to taqriban sab barabar they. siwa qiyam aur tashahud ke baithney ke."
793,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. itney mein aik shakhs aaya aur Namaz padhney laga. Namaz ke baad usne aa kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam ka jawab de kar farmaya ke wapas ja kar dobara Namaz padh, kyonke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. chunanche usne dobara Namaz padhi aur wapas aa kar phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya, aap ne us martaba bhi yahi farmaya ke dobara ja kar Namaz padh, kyonke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. teen baar isi tarah hua. aakhir us shakhs ne kaha ke us zaat ki qism ! jisne aapko maboos kya. main to us se achi Namaz nahi padh sakta. isliye aap mujhey sikhlaaiye. aap ne farmaya jab to Namaz ke liye khada ho to (pahley) takbeer keh phir Quran Majeed se jo kuchh tujh se ho sakey padh, iske baad rukoo kar aur poori tarah rukoo mein chala jaa. phir sar utha aur poori tarah khada ho jaa. phir jab to sajda karey to poori tarah sajde mein chala jaa. phir (sajde se) sar utha kar achi tarah baith jaa. dobara bhi isi tarah sajda kar. yahi tariqa Namaz ke tamam (rak'aton mein) ikhtiyar kar."
794,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo aur sajde main ( سبحانك اللهم ربنا وبحمدك , Mina اللهم اغفر لي ( padha kartey they."
795,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey to iske baad) اللهم ربنا ولك الحمد ( bhi kehtey. isi tarah jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo kartey aur sar uthatey to takbeer kehtey. donon sajdon se khadey hotey waqt bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( الله أكبر ( kaha kartey they.
796,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab imam ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( اللهم ربنا ولك الحمد ( kaho. kyonke jiska ye kehna farishton ke kehney ke sath hoga, iske pichhley tamam gunah bakhsh diye jaaeinge."
797,"lo main tumhen Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke qareeb kar doonga. chunanche Abu-Hurera (rz), zuhar, isha aur subah ki aakhiri rakaat mein qunoot padha kartey they. ( سمع الله لمن حمده (ke ba'd. yani momineen ke haq mein dua kartey aur kuffaar par laanat bhejtey ."
798,aap ne farmaya ke dua qunoot fajr aur maghrib ki namazon mein padhi jati hai.
799,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padh rahe they. jab aap rukoo se sar uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey. aik shakhs ne peechhey se kaha ( ربنا ولك الحمد , Mina حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz se farigh ho kar malum farmaya ke kis ne ye kalimaat kahey hain, us shakhs ne jawab diya ke maine. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tees se zyada farishton ko dekha ke un kalimaat ko likhney mein wo aik doosrey par sabqat ley jana chahtey they."
800,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ka tariqa batlatey they. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur jab apna sar rukoo se uthatey to itni der tak khadey rahtey ke ham sochney lagtey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhool gaey hain.
801,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rukoo', sajda, rukoo se sar uthatey waqt aur donon sajdon ke darmyan ka baithna taqriban barabar hota tha."
802,Maalik-bin-Huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) hamein (namaz padh kar) dikhlaatey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis tarah Namaz padhtey they aur ye Namaz ka waqt nahi tha. chunanche aap (eik martaba ( khadey huey aur poori tarah khadey rahe. phir jab rukoo kya aur poore itmeenaan ke sath sar uthaya tab bhi thodi der seedhey khadey rahe. abu-Qilaba ne bayan kya ke Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamarey us Shekh abu-Yazeed ki tarah Namaz padhai. abu-Yazeed jab doosrey sajde se sar uthatey to pahley achi tarah baith letey phir khadey hotey.
803,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) tamam namazon mein takbeer kaha kartey they. chahe farz hon ya na hun. Ramazan ka mahina ho ya koi aur mahina ho, chunanche jab aap Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to takbeer kehtey, rukoo mein jatey to takbeer kehtey. phir ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey aur uske baad) ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( sajde se pahley, phir jab sajde ke liye jhuktey to ( الله أكبر‏ ( kehtey. phir sajde se sar uthatey to ( الله أكبر‏ ( kehtey. phir doosra sajda kartey waqt ( الله أكبر‏ ( kehtey. isi tarah sajde se sar uthatey to ( الله أكبر‏ ( kehtey. 2 rakaat ke baad Qa'dae-Oola (do rakaat k baad baithkar attahiyaat padhne k liye baithne) ke baad jab khadey hotey tab bhi takbeer kehtey aur aap har rakaat mein aisa hi kartey yahan tak ke Namaz se farigh honey tak. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad farmatey ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tum mein sabse zyada Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz se mushabeh (similar) hun aur aap isi tarah Namaz padhtey rahe yahan tak ke aap duniya se tashrif ley gaey."
804,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sare Mubarak (rukoo' se) uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده , Mina ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( keh kar chand logon ke liye duaein kartey aur naam ley lekar farmatey. ya Allaah! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hishaam, Ayash bin abi Rabee aur tamam kamzor musalmanon ko (kuffaar se) nijat de. aey Allaah! qabila Muzar ke logon ko sakhti ke sath kuchal de aur un par qahat musallat kar jaisa ke Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein aaya tha. un dinon poorab waley qabila Muzar ke log mukhalifon mein they."
805,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se zameen par gir gaey. Sufiyan ne aksar (bajaaey ( an (an) فرس ( Mina ke) ( من فرس ( Mina kaha. us girney se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dayan pahlu zakhmi ho gaya to ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein iyaadat ki gharaz se hazir huey. itney mein Namaz ka waqt ho gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein baith kar Namaz padhai. ham bhi baith gaey. Sufiyan ne aik martaba kaha ke ham ne bhi baith kar Namaz padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh ho gaey to farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey. isliye jab wo takbeer kahey to tum bhi takbeer kaho. jab rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo. jab sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthao aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ (aur jab sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo. (Sufiyaan ne apne shagird Ali-bin madeenii se puchha ke) kya Mamar ne bhi isi tarah hadis bayan ki thi. (Ali kehtey hain ke) maine kaha ji haan. is par Sufiyan boley ke Mamar ko hadis yad thi. Zohri ne yun kaha (ولك الحمد‏). Sufiyan ne ye bhi kaha ke mujhey yad hai ke Zohri ne yun kaha aap ka dayan bazu chhil gaya tha. jab ham Zohri ke paas se nikley ibneJuraij ne kaha, main Zohri ke paas maujood tha to unhon-ne yun kaha ke aap ki dahini pindlii chhil gaee."
806,"logon ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya ham apne rab ko qiyamat mein dekh sakengey ? aap ne ( jawab ke liye) poochha, kya tumhen chaudahwiin raat ke chaand ke dekhney mein jabke iske qareeb kahin badal bhi na ho shuba hota hai? log boley hargiz nahi ya Rasulullah ! phir aap ne puchha aur kya tumhen suraj ke dekhney mein jabke iske qareeb kahin badal bhi na ho shuba hota hai. logon ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! phir aap ne farmaya ke rabbul-izzat ko tum isi tarah dekhogey. log qiyamat ke din jama kiye jaengey. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga ke jo jisey poojtaa tha wo iske sath ho jaey. chunanche bahut se log suraj ke peechhey ho lengey , bahut se chaand ke aur bahut se buton ke sath ho lengey. ye ummat baqi reh jaeygi. ismein munaafeqeen bhi hongey. phir Allah Taala aik nai sura mein aaeyga aur unse kahega ke main tumhara rab hun. wo munaafeqeen kahengey ke ham yahin apne rab ke aaney tak khadey rahengey. jab hamara rab aayega to ham usey pehchan lengey. phir izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah unke paas (aisii sura mein jisey wo pehchan lein) aaeyga aur farmaeyga ke main tumhara rab hun. wo bhi kahengey ke beshak to hamara rab hai. phir Allah Taala bulaaeyga. pul siraat jahannam ke beechon beech rakha jaeyga aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey hain ke main apni ummat ke sath us se guzarney wala sabse pahlaa rasool hoonga. us roz siwa anbiya ke koi bhi baat na kar sakega aur anbiya bhi sirf ye kahengey. aey Allaah! mujhey mehfooz rakhiyo! aey Allaah! mujhey mehfooz rakhiyo! aur jahannam mein Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah aankdey hongey. Sadan ke kaantey to tum ne dekhey hongey ? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya kaha haan ! (aap ne farmaya ( to wo Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah hongey. albatta unke tool w arz ko siwa Allah Taala ke aur koi nahi janta. ye aankdey logon ko unke aamaal ke mutabiq kheench lengey. bahut se log apne amal ki wjah se halaak hongey. bahut se tukdey-tukdey ho jaengey. phir unki nijat hogi. jahannamiyon mein se Allah Taala jis par raham farmana chaahega to malaaika ko hukm dega ke jo khalis Allah Taala hi ki ibadat kartey they unhein bahar nikaal lo. chunanche unko wo bahar nikaalengey aur ek khuda ke maannewaalon (muwahhidon) ko sajdey ke aasaar se pahchaanengey. Allah Taala ne jahannam par sajde ke aasaar ka jalaanaa haram kar diya hai. chunanche ye jab jahannam se nikaley jaeinge to asaare-sajda ke siwa unke jism ke tamam hi hisson ko aag jalaa chuki hogi. jab jahannam se bahar hongey to bilkul jal chukey hongey. isliye un par aabe-hayaat daala jaeyga jisse wo is tarah ubhar aaeingey. jaisey sailaab ke koode-karkat par sailaab ke thamney ke baad sabza ubhar aata hai. phir Allah Taala bandon ke hisab se farigh ho jaeyga lekin aik shakhs jannat aur dozakh ke darmyan ab bhi baqi reh jaeyga ye jannat mein dakhil honey wala aakhiri dozakhi shakhs hoga. iska munh dozakh ki taraf hoga. isliye kahega ke aey mere rab! mere munh ko dozakh ki taraf se pher de. kyonke uski badboo mujh ko maarey dalti hai aur uski chamak mujhey jalaaey deti hai. Allah Taala poochhega kya agar teri ye tamanna poori kar dun to to dobara koi nayaa sawal to nahi karega? banda kahega nahi teri buzurgi ki qasam! aur jaisey jaisey Allah chaahega wo qaul w qarar karega . aakhir Allah Taala jahannam ki taraf se iska munh pher dega. jab wo jannat ki taraf munh karega aur uski shadabi nazron ke samney aai to Allah ne jitni der chaha wo chup rahega. lekin phir bol padega aey Allah ! mujhey jannat ke darwazey ke qareeb pahuncha de. Allah Taala poochhega kya tu ney ahad w paiman nahi baandha tha ke us aik sawal ke siwa aur koi sawal to nahi karega. banda kahega aey mere rab! mujhey teri makhlooq mein sabse zyada bad-naseeb na hona chahiye Allah rabbul-izzat farmaeyga ke phir kya zamaanat hai ke agar teri ye tamanna poori kar di gaee to doosra koi sawal to nahi karega. banda kahega nahi teri izzat ki qism ab doosra sawal koi tujh se nahi karunga. chunanche apne rab se har tarah ahad w paiman baandhega aur jannat ke darwazey tak pahuncha diya jaeyga darwaze par pahunch kar jab jannat ki pinhaaii, taazgi aur musarraton ko dekhega to jab tak Allah Taala chaahega wo banda chup rahega. lekin aakhir bol padega ke aey Allaah! mujhey jannat ke andar pahuncha de. Allah Taala farmaeyga. afsos aey ibne-Aadam! to aisa daghaa baaz kyon bin gayaa? kya ( abhi ( tu ney ahad w paiman nahi baandha tha ke jo kuchh mujhey diya gaya, us se zyada aur kuchh na maangunga. banda kahega aey rab! mujhey apni sabse zyada bad-naseeb makhlooq na bana . Allah paak hans dega aur usey jannat mein bhi daakhile ki ijazat ata farma dega aur phir farmaeyga maang kya hai teri tamannaa. chunanche wo apni tamannaein (Allah taala ke saamney) rakhega aur jab tamam tamannaein khatm ho jaengi to Allah Taala farmaeyga ke falan cheez aur maango, falan cheez ka mazeed sawal karo. khud Allah paak hi yad dihaanii karaaega aur jab wo tamam tamannaein poori ho jaengi to farmaeyga ke tumhen ye sab aur itni hi aur di gaiin. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aur us se das guna aur zyada tumhen di gaiin. is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki yahi baat sirf mujhey yad hai ke tumhen ye tamannaein aur itni hi aur di gaiin. lekin abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine aapko ye kehtey suna tha ke ye aur uski das guna tamannaein tujh ko di gaiin."
807,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz padhtey sajdey mein apne donon baazuon ko itna phaila detey ke baghl ki safedi zahir ho jati thi. Lais-bin-Sad ne bayan kya ke mujh se bhi Jafar bin Rabeea ne isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
808,unhon-ne aik shakhs ko dekha jo rukoo aur sajda poori tarah nahi karta tha. jab wo Namaz padh chuka to unhon-ne usse farmaya ke tu ney Namaz hi nahi padhi. abu-Waeil ne kaha ke mujhey yad aata hai ke Huzefa ne ye farmaya ke agar tum mar gaey to tumhari maut Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tareeq par nahi hogii.
809,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko saat (7) aaza par sajde ka hukm diya gaya, is tarah ke na baalon ko apne samet'tey, na kapdey ko (wo saat (7) aaza ye hain) peshani (jismein naak bhi shamil hai) donon haath, donon ghutney aur donon paaun."
810,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hamein saat (7) aaza par is tarah sajde ka hukm hua hai ke ham na baal sametein na kapdey.
811,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhtey they. jab aap ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey (yani rukoo se sar uthatey ( to ham mein se koi us waqt tak apni peeth na jhukata jab tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni peshani zameen par na rakh detey.
812,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey saat (7) aaza par sajda karne ka hukm hua hai. peshani par aur apne hath se naak ki taraf ishara kya aur donon hath aur donon ghutney aur donon paon ki ungliyon par. is tarah ke ham na kapdey sametein na baal.
813,"mein Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. maine kaha ke falan nakhlistaan mein kyon na chalein sair bhi karengey aur kuchh baatein bhi karengey. chunanche aap tashrif ley chaley. abu-Salma ne bayan kya ke maine raah mein kaha ke shabe-qadr se mutaalliq aap ne agar kuchh Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai to usey bayan kijiye . unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke pahley ashrey (10 dino) mein aetikaf kya aur ham bhi aap ke sath aetikaf mein baith gaey, lekin Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aa kar bataya ke aap jiski talash mein hain (shabe-qadr) wo aagey hai. chunanche aap ne doosrey ashrey mein bhi aetikaf kya aur aap ke sath ham ne bhii. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) dobara aaey aur farmaya ke aap jiski talash mein hain wo (raat ( aagey hai. phir aap ne beeswiin Ramazan ki subah ko khutba diya. aap ne farmaya ke jisne mere sath aetikaf kya ho wo dobara kare. kyonke shabe-qadr mujhey malum ho gaee lekin main bhool gaya aur wo aakhiri ashre (10 dinon) ki taaq raaton mein hai aur maine khud ko keechad mein sajda kartey dekha. masjid ki chhat khajoor ki daaliyon ki thi. matla' bilkul saaf tha ke itney mein aik patlaa sa badal ka tukda aaya aur barasney laga. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko Namaz padhai aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peshani aur naak par keechad ka asar dekha. aap ka khuwab sachcha ho gaya."
814,kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tehband chhotey honey ki wjah se unhein gardanon se baandh kar Namaz padhtey they aur aurton se keh diya gaya tha ke jab tak mard achi tarah baith na jayen tum apne saron ko) sajda se) na uthaao.
815,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm tha ke saat (7) haddiyon par sajda karein aur baal aur kapdey na sametein .
816,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey saat (7) haddiyon par is tarah sajde ka hukm hua hai ke na baal sametoon aur na kapdey.
817,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda aur rukoo mein aksar ye padha kartey they. ( سبحانك اللهم ربنا وبحمدك , Mina اللهم اغفر لي ( (is dua ko padh kar) aap Quran ke hukm par amal kartey they."
818,main tumhen Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz kyon na sikhaa dun. abu-Qilaba ne kaha ye Namaz ka waqt nahi tha ( magar aap hamein sikhaney ke liye) khadey huey. phir rukoo kya aur takbeer kahi phir sar uthaya aur thodi der khadey rahe. phir sajda kya aur thodi der ke liye sajde se sar uthaya aur phir sajda kya aur sajde se thodi der ke liye sar uthaayaa. unhon-ne hamarey Shekh Amr-bin-Salma ki tarah Namaz padhi Ayub sakhtiyan ne kaha ke wo Amr bin Salma Namaz mein aik aisi cheez kya kartey they ke doosrey logon ko is tarah kartey maine nahi dekha. aap teesri ya chothi rakaat par) sajde se farigh ho kar khadey honey se pahley) baithtey they. (yani jalsaae-istiraahat kartey they).
819,( phir Namaz sikhlaaney ke baad Malik bin Huweris ne bayan kya ke) ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan thahrey rahe Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (behtar hai) tum apne gharon ko wapas jao. dekho ye Namaz falan waqt aur ye Namaz falan waqt padhnaa. jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to aik shakhs tum mein se azan de aur jo tum mein bada ho wo Namaz padhaaey .
820,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sajda, rukoo aur donon sajdon ke darmyan baithney ki miqdar taqriban barabar hoti thi."
821,maine jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz padhtey dekha tha bilkul isi tarah tum logon ko Namaz padhaaney mein kisi qism ki koi kami nahi chhorta hun. Sabit ne bayan kya ke Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) aik aisa amal kartey they jisey main tumhen kartey nahi dekhta . jab wo rukoo se sar uthatey to itni der tak khadey rahtey ke dekhney wala samajhta ke bhool gaey hain aur isi tarah donon sajdon ke darmyan itni der tak baithtey rahtey ke dekhney wala samajhta ke bhool gaey hain.
822,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sajde mein aetidaal ka khayal rakho aur apne bazu kutton ki tarah na phailaayaa karo.
823,aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz padhtey dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab taaq rakaat mein hotey to us waqt tak na uthtey jab tak thodi der baith na letey.
824,mein Namaz padha raha hun lekin meri niyat kisi farz ki adaaeygi nahi hai balke mein sirf tum ko ye dikhaana chahta hun ke Nabi Karim kis tarah Namaz padha kartey they. Ayub sakhtiyan ne bayan kya ke maine abu-Qilaba se puchha ke Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kis tarah Namaz padhtey they? to unhon-ne farmaya ke hamarey Shekh Amr bin Salma ki tarah . Ayub ne bayan kya ke Shekh tamam takbeerein kehtey they aur jab doosrey sajde se sar uthatey to thodi der baithtey aur zameen ka sahara lekar phir uthtey.
825,hamein Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz padhai aur jab unhon-ne sajde se sar uthaya to pukar kar takbeer kahi phir jab sajda kya to aisa hi kya phir sajde se sar uthaya to bhi aisa hi kya isi tarah jab 2 rakatein padh kar khadey huey us waqt bhi aap ne buland awaz se takbeer kahi aur farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha.
826,"maine aur Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi. aap ne jab sajda kya, sajde se sar uthaya 2 rakaton ke baad khadey huey to har martaba takbeer kahi . jab aap ne salam pher diya to Imran-bin-Husain ne mera hath pakad kar kaha ke unhon-ne waqei hamein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah Namaz padhai hai ya ye kaha ke mujhey unhon-ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz yad dila di."
827,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko wo hamesha dekhtey ke aap Namaz mein chaar-zaanoo baithtey hain mein abhi nau-umr tha maine bhi isi tarah karna shuru kar diya lekin Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se rokaa aur farmaya ke Namaz mein sunnat ye hai ke) tashahud mein) dayan paon khada rakhey aur bayan phaila de maine kaha ke aap to usi ( meri ( tarah kartey hain aap boley ke) kamzori ki wjah se) mere paon mera bojh nahi utha patey .
828,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand ashaab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath baithey huey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ka zikr honey laga to abu Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz tum sabse zyada yad hai maine aapko dekha ke jab aap takbeer kehtey to apne hathon ko kandhon tak ley jatey, jab aap rukoo kartey to ghutnon ko apne hathon se poori tarah pakad letey aur peeth ko jhukaa detey. phir jab rukoo se sar uthatey to is tarah seedhey khadey ho jatey ke tamam jod seedhey ho jatey. jab aap sajda kartey to aap apne hathon ko) zameen par) is tarah rakhtey ke na bilkul phailey huey hotey aur na simte huey. paon ki ungliyon ke munh qible ki taraf rakhtey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakaton ke baad baithtey to baain paon par baithtey aur dayan paon khada rakhtey aur jab aakhiri rakaat mein baithtey baain paon ko aagey kar letey aur daain ko khada kar detey phir maqad (peeth) par baithtey . Leis ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se aur Yazeed bin Muhammad-bin Halhala se suna aur Muhammad-bin Halhala ne ibne- ata se, aur Abu-Saleh ne Leis se ( كل فقار مكانه ( naql kya hai aur ibne-Mubarak ne Yahya bin Ayub se bayan kya unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se Yazeed bin abii-Habeeb ne bayan kya ke Muhammad-bin Amr bin-Halhala ne unse hadis main ( كل فقار ( bayan kya."
829,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Zohar ki Namaz padhai aur 2 rakaton par baithney ke bajaey khadey ho gaey, chunanche sarey log bhi unke sath khadey ho gaey, jab Namaz khatm honey wali thi aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke salam pherney ka intizar kar rahe they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( الله أكبر‏ ( kaha aur salam pherney se pahley 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera ."
830,hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-zuhar padhai. aapko chahiye tha baithna lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (bhool kar) khadey ho gaey phir Namaz ke aakhir mein baithey hi baithey 2 sajdey kiye.
831,"jab ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhtey to kehtey ( tarjama ( salam ho Jibraeel aur Mikaail par salam ho falan aur falan par) Allah par salam ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik roz hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya Allah to khud '' salam '' hai. (tum Allah ko kya salam kartey ho ( isliye jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey to ye kahey التحيات لله ، Mina والصلوات والطيبات ، Mina Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين tamaam aadaabe-bandagii, tamam ibaadatein aur tamam behtreen ta'reefein Allah ke liye hain. aap par salam ho aey Nabi aur Allah ki rahmatein aur uski barkatein ham par salam aur Allah ke tamam Saleh bandon par salaam. jab tum ye kahogey to tumhara salam aasman w zameen mein jahan koi Allah ka nek banda hai usko pahunch jaeyga mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uske bandey aur rasool hain."
832,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein ye dua padhtey theyاللهم إني أعوذ بك من عذاب القبر وأعوذ بك من فتنة المسيح الدجال ، Mina وأعوذ بك من فتنة المحيا وفتنة الممات ، Mina اللهم إني أعوذ بك من المأثم والمغرم aey Allah qabr ke azab se main teri panah mangta hun. zindagi ke aur maut ke fitnon se teri panah mangta hun. dajjal ke fitne se teri panah mangta hun aur aey Allah main teri panah mangta hun gunahon se aur qarz se. kisi (yani Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ( ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to qarz se bahut hi zyada panah maangtey hain ! is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi maqrooz ho jaey to wo jhoot boltaa hai aur wada khilaf ho jata hai.
833,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz mein dajjal ke fitney se panah maangtey suna.
834,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey koi aisi dua sikhaa dijiye jisey main Namaz mein padha karun. aap ne farmaya ke ye dua padha karo (اللهم إني zulmat نفسي ظلما كثيرا wla يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت ، Mina فاغفر لي مغفرة من عندك ، Mina وارحمني إنك أنت الغفور الرحيم )aey Allah ! maine apni jaan par) gunah karke ( bahut zyada zulm kya to gunahon ko terey siwa koi doosra maaf karne wala nahi. mujhey apne paas se bharpur maghfirat ata farma aur mujh par raham karke maghfirat karne wala aur raham karne wala beshak w shuba to hi hai.
835,(pahley ( jab ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey to ham ( Qada mein) ye kaha kartey they ke iske bandon ki taraf se Allah par salam ho aur falan par aur falan par salam ho. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye na kaho ke ''Allah par salam ho'' kyonke Allah to khud salam hai. balke ye kaho (التحيات لله ، Mina والصلوات والطيبات ، Mina Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين‏)aadaabe-bandagaan aur tamam ibaadatein aur tamam pakeeza khairaatein Allah hi ke liye hain aap par aey Nabi salam ho aur Allah ki rahmatein aur barkatein nazil hon ham par aur Allah ke Saleh bandon par salam ho aur jab tum ye kaho gey to aasman par Allah ke tamam bandon ko pahunchega Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aasman aur zameen ke darmyan tamam bandon ko pahunchey ga (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله)mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uske bandey aur rasool hain. iske baad dua ka ikhtiyar hai jo usey pasand ho kare.
836,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko keechad mein sajda kartey huey dekha. mitti ka asar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peshani par saaf zahir tha.
837,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (namaz se) salam phertey to salam ke khatm hotey hi auratein khadi ho jaatiin ( bahar aaney ke liye) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey honey se pahley thodi der thahrey rahtey they. ibne-Shahab (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha, main samajhta hun aur pura ilm to Allah hi ko hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isliye thahar jatey they ke auratein jaldi chali jayen aur mard Namaz se farigh ho kar unko na paaein."
838,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to ham ne bhi salam pheraa.
839,mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) poori tarah yad hain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mere ghar ke dol se kulli karna bhi yad hai (jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere munh mein dali thi).
840,main apni qaum bani Salim ki imamat kya karta tha. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! meri aankh kharaab ho gaee hai aur (barsaat mein) pani se bharey huey naley mere aur meri qaum ki masjid ke beech mein rukawat bin jatey hain. main chahta hun ke aap mere makan par tashrif la kar kisi aik jagah Namaz ada farmaein taake main usey apni Namaz ke liye muqarrar kar loon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke insha-Allah taala mein tumhari khahish poori karunga subah ko jab din chadh gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (andar aaney ki) ijazat chahi aur maine de di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey nahi balke puchha ke ghar ke kis hisse mein Namaz padhwaanaa chahtey ho. aik jagah ki taraf jisey maine Namaz padhney ke liye pasand kya tha. ishara kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz ke liye) khadey huey aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf banai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to ham ne bhi pheraa.
841,"buland awaz se zikr, farz Namaz se farigh honey par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane Mubarak mein jari tha."
842,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz khatm honey ko takbeer (Allaahu-akbar) ki wjah se samajh jata tha. Ali-bin madeenii ne kaha ke ham se Sufiyan ne Amr ke hawale se bayan kya ke abu-Ma'bad Ibne-Abbas ke ghulaamon mein sabse zyada qaabile-bharosa they. Ali-bin madeenii ne bataya ke unka naam Nafiz tha.
843,"naadaar log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke ameer w raees log buland darjaat aur hamesha rehney wali jannat hasil kar chukey halanke jis tarah ham Namaz padhtey hain wo bhi padhtey hain aur jaisey ham rozey rakhtey hain wo bhi rakhtey hain lekin maal w daulat ki wjah se unhein ham par fauqiyat hasil hai ke uski wjah se wo Haj kartey hain. Umra kartey hain. jihad kartey hain aur sadqey detey hain (aur ham mohtaajii ki wjah se in kaamon ko nahi kar paatey) is par aap ne farmaya ke lo main tumhen aik aisa amal bataataa hon ke agar tum uski pabandi karogey to jo log tum se aagey badh chukey hain unhein tum paalo gey aur tumharey martabe tak phir koi nahi pahunch sakta aur tum sabse achchhey ho jaogey siwa unke jo yahi amal shuru kar dein har Namaz ke baad 33-33 martaba tasbeeh (Sub'haanAllah), Mina tahmeed (الحمد لله), Mina takbeer ( الله أكبر ( kaha karo. phir ham mein ikhtilaf ho gaya kisi ne kaha ke ham tasbeeh ( sub'haanAllah) tentis martaba , tahmeed ( الحمد لله ( tentis martaba aur takbeer ( الله أكبر ( chauntis martaba kahengey. maine is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se dobara malum kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) sub'haanAllah) , Mina ( الحمد لله (aur ( الله أكبر ( kaho yahan tak ke har aik unmein se tentis martaba ho jaey."
844,"mujh se Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik khat mein likhwaayaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har farz Namaz ke baad ye dua padhtey they (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ، Mina padhi. له الملك ، Mina padhi. وله الحمد ، Mina padhi. وهو على كل شىء قدير ، Mina padhi. اللهم لا مانع لما أعطيت ، Mina padhi. wla معطي لما منعت ، Mina padhi. wla ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد)Allaah ke siwa koi laaiqe-ibaadat nahi. iska koi Sharik nahi. badhshahat uski hai aur tamam tareef usi ke liye hai. wo har cheez par qaadir hai. aey Allah jisey to de usse rokney wala koi nahi aur jisey to na de usey dene wala koi nahi aur kisi maaldaar ko uski daulat w maal teri bargah mein koi nafa na pahuncha sakengey. Shoba ne bhi Abdul-Malik se isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Hasan ne farmaya ke) hadis mein lafz ( ) جد (ke mana maal daari ke hain aur hukm, Qasim bin mukhaimira se wo Warraad ke waastey se isi tarah riwayat kartey hain."
845,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz (farz) padha chuktey to hamari taraf munh kartey.
846,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Hudaibiya mein subah ki Namaz padhai aur raat ko barish ho chuki thi Namaz se farigh honey ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ki taraf munh kya aur farmaya malum hai tumharey rab ne kya farmaya hai. logon ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool khub jantey hain (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) tumharey rab ka irshad hai ke subah hui to mere kuchh bandey mujh par eman laey aur kuchh mere munkar huey jisne kaha ke Allah ke Fazal aur uski rehmat se hamarey liye barish hui to wo mera momin hai aur sitaron ka munkir aur jisne kaha ke falan taarey ke fulaanii jagah par aaney se barish hui wo mera munkir hai aur sitaron ka momin.
847,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik raat ( isha ki) Namaz mein der farmai taqriban aadhi raat tak. phir aakhir hujre se bahar tashrif laey aur Namaz ke baad hamari taraf munh kya aur farmaya ke doosrey log Namaz padh kar so chukey lekin tum log jab tak Namaz ka intizar kartey rahe maano ke Namaz mein rahe (yani tum ko Namaz ka sawab milta raha ( .
848,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) nafl ( usi jagah par padhtey they aur jis jagah farz padhtey aur Qasim-bin-Muhammad -bin-abi-Bakr ne bhi isi tarah kya hai aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan riwayat hai ke imam apni ( farz padhney ki) jagah par nafl na padhey aur ye sahi nahi.
849,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab salam phertey to kuchh der apni jagah par baithey rehtey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha Allah behtar janey ham to ye samajhtey hain ke ye aap isliye kartey they taake auratein pahley chali jaaein.
850,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) salam phertey to auratein lot kar janey lagtiin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uthney se pahley apne gharon mein dakhil ho chuki hotiin.
851,"maine Madina main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein aik martaba Asr ki Namaz padhi. salam pherney ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaldi se uth khadey huey aur safon ko cheertey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni kisi biwi ke hujre mein gaey. log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki us tezi ki wjah se ghabraa gaey. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur jaldi ki wjah se logon ke tajjub ko mehsus farmaya to farmaya ke hamarey paas aik soney ka dala ( taqseem karne se) bach gaya tha mujhey usmein dil laga rehna bura malum hua, maine iske baant dene ka hukm de diyaa.`"
852,koi shakhs apni Namaz mein se kuchh bhi shaitan ka hissa na lagaey is tarah ke dahini taraf hi lautnaa apne liye zaroori qarar de ley. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aksar baain taraf se laut'tey dekha.
853,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-khaibar ke mauqe par kaha tha ke jo shakhs us darakht yani lehsun ko khaaey huey ho usey hamari masjid mein na aana chahiye (kachchaa lehsun ya piyaz khana murad hai ke us se munh mein bo paida ho jati hai).
854,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs ye darakht khaaey (aap ki murad lehsun se thi) to wo hamari masjid mein na aaey Ata ne kaha maine Jaabir se puchha ke aap ki murad us se kya thi. unhon-ne jawab diya ke aap ki murad sirf kachchey lehsun se thi. Mukhlid bin Yazeed ne ibne-Juraij ke waaste se ( الانیہ ke bajaey) الانتنہ naql kya hai (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad sirf lehsun ki badboo se thi).
855,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo lehsun ya piyaz khaaey huey ho to wo ham se door rahe ya (ye kaha ke usey ( hamari masjid se door rehna chahiye ya usey apne ghar mein hi baithna chahiye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik handi laai gaee jis mein kai qism ki harii tarkaariyaan thin. (piyaaz ya gandanaa bhi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein bo mehsus ki aur uske mutaalliq malum kya. us saalan mein jitni tarkaariyaan dali gaee thin wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bata di gaiin. wahan aik sahabi maujood they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski taraf ye saalan badha do. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khana pasand nahi farmaya aur farmaya ke tum log kha lo. meri jin se sargoshi rehti hai tumhari nahi rehti aur Ahmed bin Saleh ne ibne- Wahab se yun naql kya ke thaal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laai gaee thi. ibne-Wahab ne kaha ke tabaq jis mein harii tarkaariyaan thin aur Leis aur abu-Safwaan ne Yunus se riwayat mein handi ka qissa nahi bayan kya hai. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne (ya Saeed ya ibne- Wahab ne kaha ( mein nahi keh sakta ke ye khud Zohri ka qaul hai ya hadis mein dakhil hai.
856,aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se lehsun ke barey mein kya suna hai. unhon-ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs us darakht ko khaaey wo hamarey qareeb na aaey hamarey sath Namaz na padhey .
857,jo (eik martaba ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik akelii alag thalag tooti hui qabr par se guzar rahe they wahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf baandhey huey they. Sulaiman ne kaha ke maine Shabi se puchha ke abu-Amr aap se ye kis ne bayan kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne.
858,unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Juma ke din har baligh ke liye ghusl zaroori hai.
859,"aik raat main apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan soyaa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi wahan so gaey. phir raat ka aik hissey jab guzar gaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur aik latkii hui mashk se halka sa wuzu kya. Amr ( rawi hadis ne) us wuzu ko bahut hi halka batlaya (yani usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bahut kam pani istemal farmaya ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey huey iske baad maine bhi uth kar isi tarah wuzu kya jaisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf khada ho gaya. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dahini taraf pher diya phir Allah Taala ne jitna chaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) let rahe phir so gaey. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kharraatey leney lagey. aakhir muazzan ne aa kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ki khabar di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske sath Namaz ke liye tashrif le gaey aur Namaz padhai magar ( nayaa ( wuzu nahi kya Sufiyan ne kaha, ham ne Amr-bin-Dinar se kaha ke log kehtey hain ke (sotey waqt) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) sirf ( aankhen soti thin lekin dil nahi sota tha. Amr-bin-Dinar ne jawab diya ke maine Ubaid-bin-Umair se suna wo kehtey they ke anbiya ka khuwab bhi wahiy hota hai phir Ubaid ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) إني أرى في المنام أني أذبحك‏ ( ) tarjama ( maine khuwab dekha hai ke tumhen zabah kar raha hun."
860,(unki maan) Ishaq ki daadi Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya jisey unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bataur-ziyaafat taiyaar kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana khaya phir farmaya ke chalo main tumhen Namaz padha dun. hamarey yahan aik boriyaa tha jo puraanaa honey ki wjah se siyah ho gaya tha. maine usey pani se saaf kya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur (peechhey) mere sath yateem ladka (zameera-bin-Sa'd) khada hua. meri boodhi daadi (mulaika Umme-Sulaim) hamarey peechhey khadi huin phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padhai.
861,main aik gadhi par Sawar ho kar aaya. abhi main jawaanii ke qareeb tha ( lekin baligh na tha) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein logon ko Namaz padha rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney diwar wghaira ( aad ( na thi. main saf ke aik hissey ke aagey se guzar kar utraa. gadhi charney ke liye chhod di aur khud saf mein shamil ho gaya. kisi ne mujh par aetraz nahi kya (halanke mein nabaligh thaa).
862,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik raat isha mein der ki aur Ayash ne ham se Abdul-Aala se bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Mamar ne Zohri se bayan kya, unse Urwa ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha mein aik martaba der ki. yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne awaz di ke auratein aur bachchey so gaey. unhon-ne farmaya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar aaey aur farmaya ke (is waqt) poori zameen par tumharey siwa aur koi us Namaz ko nahi padhta , us zamane mein Madina walon ke siwa aur koi Namaz nahi padhta tha."
863,"kya tum ne ( aurton ka ( nikalnaa eid ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath dekha hai? unhon-ne kaha haan dekha hai agar main aap ka rishtedar azeez na hota to kabhi na dekhta (yani meri kam-umrii aur qaraabat ki wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh ko apne sath rakhtey they) Kasir bin Salat ke makan ke paas jo nishan hai pahley wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba sunaya phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ke paas tashrif laey aur unhein bhi wa'z-w-naseehat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse khairat karne ke liye kaha, chunanche aurton ne apne chhalley aur anguthiyan utaar-utaar kar Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein daalnii shuru kar diye. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ghar tashrif laey."
864,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba isha ki Namaz mein itni der ki ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehna padaa ke auratein aur bachchey so gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hujrey se) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke dekho poori zameen par us Namaz ka (is waqt) tumharey siwa aur koi intizar nahi kar raha hai. un dinon Madina ke siwa aur kahin Namaz nahi padhi jati thi aur log isha ki Namaz shafaq doobney ke baad se raat ki pehli tehai guzarney tak padha kartey they.
865,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari beeviyan tum se raat mein masjid aaney ki ijazat maangein to tum log unhein uski ijazat de diya karo. Ubaidullah ke sath us hadis ko Shoba ne bhi Aamash se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
866,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein auratein farz Namaz se salam pherney ke fauran baad (baahar aaney ke liye) uth jati thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mard Namaz ke baad apni jagah baithey rehtey. jab tak Allah ko manzoor hota. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthtey to doosrey mard bhi khadey ho jatey.
867,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padh letey phir auratein chaadrein lapet kar (apne gharon ko) wapas ho jati thin. andherey se unki pehchan na ho saktii.
868,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Namaz ke liye khada hota hun, mera irada ye hota hai ke Namaz lambi karun lekin kisi bachchey ke roney ki awaz sun kar Namaz ko mukhtasar kar deta hun ke mujhey uski maan ko takleef dena bura malum hota hai."
869,aaj aurton mein jo nai baatein paida ho gaee hain agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein dekh letey to unko masjid mein aaney se rok detey jis tarah Bani-Israeel ki aurton ko rok diya gaya tha. maine puchha ke kya Bani-Israeel ki aurton ko rok diya gaya tha? aap ne farmaya ke haan.
870,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab salam phertey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke salam phertey hi auratein janey ke liye uth jati thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der thahrey rahtey khadey na hotey. Zohri ne kaha ke ham ye samajhtey hain, aagey Allah jaaney, ye isliye tha taake auratein mardon se pahley nikal jaaein."
871,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (meri maan) Umme-Sulaim ke ghar mein Namaz padhai. main aur yateem mil kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey huey aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey peechhey thin.
872,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz munh andherey padhtey they. musalmanon ki auratein jab (namaz padh kar) wapas hotiin to andherey ki wjah se unki pehchan na hoti ya wo aik dusri ko na pehchan saktiin.
873,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se kisi ki biwi (namaz padhney ke liye masjid mein aaney ki) us se ijazat maangey to shauhar ko chahiye ke usko na rokey.
874,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( meri maan ( Umme-Sulaim ke ghar mein Namaz padhai. main aur yateem mil kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey huey aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey peechhey thin.
875,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab salam phertey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke salam phertey hi auratein janey ke liye uth jati thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der thahrey rahtey khadey na hotey. Zohri ne kaha ke ham ye samajhtey hain, aagey Allah jaaney, ye isliye tha taake auratein mardon se pahley nikal jaaein."
